com.safenetinc.jcprov.constants

Enum HsmPolicy

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<HsmPolicy>
      • com.safenetinc.jcprov.constants.HsmPolicy
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<HsmPolicy>

    public enum HsmPolicy
extends java.lang.Enum<HsmPolicy>
    Enum defining a list of supported HSM policy list. The list of policies are extracted from the following C header file: /interfaces/Include/firmware/luna2if.h The values listed in this enum must be in sync with luna2if.h header file. That is, every new option that is added in the header file must be included here too. The same applies for JavaSP HSM Policy settings.
